{"tid":508704,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[生日快樂] 到底耶穌喺幾時出世？","createTime":"2017-12-24T13:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T06:24:45.000Z","uid":132025,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10b728e84f31c6a5e5bb09d0177d840f79b59d7f","tid":508704,"uid":132025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:40:27.000Z","msg":"話說12月25日喺聖誕節，聖嬰誕生。<br />\n但係公元記年法又係計耶穌出世開始，咁啫喺耶穌本應喺元年1月1日出世。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人理論：時間同空間構成時空概念，根據quantum mechanics，一粒particle可以superposition同時存在喺不同空間，同時存在喺不同時間亦有可能。所以初生耶穌全部嘅粒子同時存在喺BC1年12月25日同AD1年1月1日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求指教<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b012d0ee46fbc52564865cd9e9a8d9417d34bf","tid":508704,"uid":3180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:48:09.000Z","msg":"唔係夏天出世咩"},{"pid":"d20e5bb9f35b34265a6cd4f9f113e79566862c01","tid":508704,"uid":132025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係夏天出世咩</blockquote><br />\n認真咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059710eb6a79b122d5bb98378532a562f0a7637c","tid":508704,"uid":37054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"聖誕係耶仔出世 1月1係佛祖誕生"},{"pid":"acfb66914307c17de53bc8d271a6e32c81344398","tid":508704,"uid":35815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"